titles.title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Fourteenth Congressional District of Florida.
Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Fourteenth Congressional District of Florida.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 119-51, by Mr. Steil.

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 16.

action.text: Mr. Steil asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.
